Class OntologyExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.neu.ece.devicedescriptiongenerator.extractor.OntologyExtractor

  • public class OntologyExtractor
extends java.lang.Object
    As one of the most important classes of the program, OntologyExtractor defines ontology extractor used for extracting OWL axioms from input ontology.
